note for Spheroid "STANDALONE — no Cell base class.\ndraw() uses simulationConfig.cell_color (1.0),\nNOT per-cell _brightness.\n_brightness stored but unused.\nSrc: src/Spheroid.cpp (~658 lines)"

note for Frame "L2 cost (NORM_L2) + overlap penalty.\n_currentCost cached to avoid redundant L2.\nperturbCell uses computeOverlapForCell (O(n)).\ntrySplitCell burn-in uses overlap penalty.\nSrc: src/Frame.cpp (~423 lines)"

note for CellUniverse "Unified stochastic loop in optimize().\nP(split) from PREVIOUS frame PCA elongation.\nPre-opt shapes saved for trySplitCell.\nSplit blacklist prevents redundant burn-ins.\npreviousElongations stored end-of-frame.\nSrc: src/CellUniverse.cpp (~498 lines)"

note for BaseConfig "cell is unique_ptr~SpheroidConfig~.\nRule of Five: copy ctor deep-copies,\nmove ctor/assign = default."

note for MainModule "Preprocessing pipeline:\n1. BGR→Gray, normalize [0,1]\n2. Gaussian blur (sigma=10)\n3. Auto-calibrate sigmoid center from bg zone\n4. Sigmoid: 1/(1+exp(-75*(x-center)))\n5. Z-interpolation (33→225 slices)"
